I have followed the instructions [laid out here](https://github.com/FortAwesome/font-awesome-sass) but when I look at my compiled CSS the expected unicode numbers have been replaced by boxes:

```CSS
.fa-glass:before {
  content: "";
}
```

instead of

```CSS
